textAfterTable: Booking Conditions Booking Conditions A deposit of 50% of the total room hire is payable on booking. The balance of room hire is payable three months prior to the event. No refunds will be paid in the event of a cancellation. Charges for additional facilities and catering must be paid seven days prior to the event. Sutton Coldfield Town Hall is a non smoking venue.
